    "The 9 × 9 orange dots in the material domain are the locations of the sensors.",
    "The resulting wave field forms a 9 × 9 × 2000-shaped array.",
    "For each sample, a binarized image shows the ground-truth crack existence.",
    "The original image resolution is 100 × 100, in alignment with the mesh size used by dLEM."
